    • 方法详细资料

      • write

        void write(org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.data.api.YangInstanceIdentifier path,
           org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.data.api.schema.NormalizedNode<?,?> data)
        已过时。 
        Store a provided data at specified path. This acts as a add / replace operation, which is to say that whole subtree will be replaced by specified path.

        If you need add or merge of current object with specified use merge(YangInstanceIdentifier, NormalizedNode).

        参数:
        path - the path to write
        data - data object to be written
        抛出:
        IllegalStateException - if the client code already sealed transaction and invoked ready()
